SA: Summer Art Program 2018 ( Session- I ) > 29th May to 30th June 2018|website=Delhi Events|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref>.\n* \"To The End of Land\"  - Contemporary Art from Israel From 28 April 2018, The National Gallery of Modern Art, New Delhi.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pib.gov.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=179003|title=Israeli Modern Art Exhibition inagurated in the capital, today|website=pib.gov.in|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://embassies.gov.il/delhi/AboutTheEmbassy/Culture/Pages/To-the-End-of-the-Land---Contemporary-Art-from-Israel-.aspx|website=embassies.gov.il|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref>\n* \"EMINENT PRINTMAKERS OF INDIA\" as part of First Print Biennial India 2018 at National Gallery of Modern Art, New Delhi. From 27 March to 22 April 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pib.gov.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=177997|title=The first International Exhibition of Graphic Prints 'Print Biennale India 2018' inaugurated in New Delhi today|website=pib.gov.in|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref>\n* \"Songs of the Uncaged Birds\" at National Gallery of Modern Art, New Delhi. Inaugurated on 8 March 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.delhievents.com/2018/03/exhibition-songs-uncaged-birds-ngma-women-day.html|title=EXHIBITION 'Songs of the Uncaged Birds' > 8th March 2018 onwards|website=Delhi Events|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref>\n* \"ANZAC Centenary Print Portfolio\" at National Gallery of Modern Art, New Delhi. Inaugurated on 11 March 2018<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.delhievents.com/2018/03/exhibition-anzac-centenary-print-portfolio-ngma-india-gate.html|title=EXHIBITION \"ANZAC Centenary Print Portfolio\" > 11th March 2018 onwards|website=Delhi Events|access-date=2019-10-28}}</ref>\n* \"CODICI...CODICI A TRATTI...FONTE\" at National Gallery of Modern Art, New Delhi, Opened on 15 March 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://iicnewdelhi.esteri.it/iic_newdelhi/en/gli_eventi/calendario/2018/03/codici-exhibition-integration-of.html|title=Codi